Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: pyknx
Version: 0.0.3
Summary: Python bindings for KNX
Home-page: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pyknx/
Author: Cyrille Defranoux
Author-email: knx@aminate.net
License: GNU Public General License
Description: Pyknx provides modules that ease interacting with a linknx server. It allows to read or write objects configuration or object values. It also implements a communicator daemon that can be used to receive events from linknx (through ioports).
Platform: UNKNOWN
